         <abstract id="aspace_c879e6c30603b7003a1e469b4fc8984c">Diary, diplomas, and miscellaneous papers, chiefly documenting Hervey D. Leland's periods of service as a teacher in Japan. The diary (1909) was written while he was teaching English in Iwakuni, Japan.</abstract>
